Package: aire.zmvm
Type: Package
Title: Download pollution data for the Zona Metropolitana del Valle de Mexico
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Diego Valle-Jones
Maintainer: Diego Valle-Jones <diego@diegovalle.net>
Description: Downloads pollution data for the Mexico City metro area. This package can download
    the daily maximum, minimum, or average for each of the pollution measuring stations
    in the Zona Metropolitana del Valle de Mexico.
License: CC0
LazyData: TRUE
